vectorization (addVectorPasses), LoopSinkPass\n\n## Execution Order in O2/O3 Pipeline\n\nThe standard optimization pipeline for O2 and O3 follows this order:\n\n1. **Module Simplification Phase**:\n   - Annotation2MetadataPass\n   - ForceFunctionAttrsPass\n   - InferFunctionAttrsPass, CoroEarlyPass\n   - Function-level simplification (EarlyCSE, SROA, SimplifyCFG)\n   - CallSiteSplittingPass (O3 only)\n   - IPSCCPPass, GlobalOptPass, DeadArgumentEliminationPass\n   - Function attribute inference (FunctionAttrsPass)\n   - Jump threading, GVN, DSE\n\n2. **Module Inlining Phase**:\n   - ModuleInlinerWrapperPass with CGSCC passes\n   - Post-inlining simplification\n\n3. **Module Optimization Phase**:\n   - PartialInlinerPass\n   - ReversePostOrderFunctionAttrsPass\n   - Function optimization pipeline:\n     - Loop optimizations (LoopRotate, LoopDeletion, LoopInterchange)\n     - Loop fusion, distribution\n     - Vectorization (SLP, Loop vectorization)\n     - ControlHeightReductionPass (O3 only)\n     - LoopSinkPass\n   - Final SimplifyCFG and instruction combining\n\n## Key Files Summary\n\n- **llvm/include/llvm/IR/PassManager.h**: Core template and ModulePassManager definition\n- **llvm/include/llvm/PassRegistry.h**: PassRegistry declaration\n- **llvm/lib/IR/PassRegistry.cpp**: Pass registration implementation\n- **llvm/include/llvm/PassInfo.h**: PassInfo metadata structure\n- **llvm/include/llvm/PassSupport.h**: Registration macros and RegisterPass template\n- **llvm/include/llvm/IR/PassManagerInternal.h**: PassConcept and PassModel implementations\n- **llvm/include/llvm/Passes/PassBuilder.h**: PassBuilder API declaration\n- **llvm/lib/Passes/PassBuilderPipelines.cpp**: Pipeline construction implementations\n- **llvm/include/llvm/InitializePasses.h**: Pass initialization declarations"
